╚IN LOVING MEMORY OF OUR WONDERFUL MUM
A LIFETIME OF LOVE AND DEVOTION
HOW PRIVILEGED WE WERE
FOR GUIDING US THROUGH THE YEARS WHEN WE WERE YOUNG
SHOWING US THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN RIGHT AND WRONG
LOVING US THOUGH SOMETIMES WE LET YOU DOWN
FOR FORGIVING US WHEN WE WERE NOWHERE TO BE FOUND
GOOD NIGHT AND GOD BLESS BEAUTIFUL ANGEL
WE MISS YOU SO VERY VERY MUCH
SUSAN, PETER, ALAN AND ROBERT

IN LOVING MEMORY oF
TWIZZLE
LESLEY JANE MABON
YOU'D ARRIVE WITH THE MORNING SUN
AND WITH THE MIDNIGHT TIDE YOU WOULD LEAVE
JUST WHEN I NEEDED YOU MORE THAN ANYONE
MORE THAN ANYONE EVER NEEDED ME
GOOD NIGHT AND GOD BLESS MY DARLING
INTO PARADISE MAY THE ANGELS LEAD YOU
WILL NEVER STOP LOVING YOU   ALAN"╠
